cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.AI, cs.LG. 

The paper deals with image processing and computer vision, specifically single-image super-resolution (SISR) and texture enhancement. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves generating high-resolution images, which falls under the category of graphics (cs.GR). The use of deep neural networks (DNNs) for SISR suggests that the paper could also be classified under machine learning (cs.MM) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper proposes a novel framework for texture enhancement, which could be considered as a contribution to the field of image processing and computer graphics, and thus could be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning).
